[genericglass Collins] Serving Glass: Collins With Ice

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
1 oz [genericingredient Triple Sec] Hiram Walker Triple Sec
1/2 oz [genericingredient Bourbon] Jim Beam Bourbon
1/2 oz [genericingredient Southern Comfort] Southern Comfort
1/2 oz Grenadine
Splash [genericingredient Pineapple Juice] Pineapple Juice
Dash [genericingredient Tabasco] Tabasco
Shake and Strain
Fill [genericingredient cranberry juice] Ocean Spray Cranberry Juice
Garnish: Cherry

